250
00:11:54,760 --> 00:11:55,780
A good guy?

251
00:11:56,080 --> 00:11:56,710
What's wrong?

252
00:11:57,560 --> 00:11:58,960
Do you know what his nickname is?

253
00:11:59,010 --> 00:12:00,800
