499
00:24:23,880 --> 00:24:25,200
I had planned to start working.

500
00:24:25,560 --> 00:24:26,840
But my professor insisted that

501
00:24:26,880 --> 00:24:28,440
I get my PhD instead.

502
00:24:28,520 --> 00:24:29,800
